overview: "The user wanted to significantly enhance the visual appeal of their
  sleep questionnaire app. The agent performed a detailed aesthetic review,
  identifying a need for a more calming and professional design. The approach
  involved a complete overhaul of the app's visual language: a new sleep-themed
  color palette was implemented, core UI components were redesigned, and all
  questionnaire sections were updated for consistent styling. This included
  replacing generic gray boxes with refined card-style groupings, enhancing
  interactive form elements, and improving the overall layout. Additionally, a
  console error related to null values in input fields was identified and
  resolved. The outcome is a much more polished, cohesive, and appropriate
  interface for a sleep health application."
